# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  External sources cloned outside the repo
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Cloned whisper.cpp upstream — external source, not versioned here.
# Used to rebuild Deckle.Whisp's native runtime (libwhisper.dll +
# ggml-*.dll) on demand ; binaries land in %LOCALAPPDATA%\Deckle\native\,
# never in the repo. Runtime model weights similarly live under
# %LOCALAPPDATA%\Deckle\models\, sourced by the first-run wizard.
whisper.cpp/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Build artifacts
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# .NET build output.
src/**/bin/
src/**/obj/

# Deployment output — rebuildable via dotnet publish.
publish/

# Misc build logs.
build-log.txt
**/build.log
**/*.binlog
**/xamlcompiler.log
**/xaml.out

# MSBuild leftovers occasionally written outside bin/obj.
**/*.tlog
**/*.lastbuildstate
MSBuild_*.failure.txt

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  IDE / OS junk
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Visual Studio local state.
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userprefs
*.vsidx

# JetBrains, Vim swap, macOS, Windows Explorer thumbnails.
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# VSCode Local History extension.
.history/

# Backup / patch / merge leftovers.
*.bak
*.backup
*.old
*.orig
*.rej
.~lock.*

# Aider AI session state — may contain private context.
.aider*

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Secrets / credentials — preventive, no such file should ever exist here
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Environment variable files.
*.env
.env
.env.*
.envrc

# Private keys, certificates, secret stores.
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.secret
*.secrets
secrets/
credentials*
*.credential
auth.json
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
id_ecdsa*
id_dsa*

# Cloud / container credentials.
.aws/
.gcloud/
.docker/config.json
*.kubeconfig
kubeconfig

# Local config overrides — Microsoft / .NET conventions.
appsettings.local.json
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.development.json
local.settings.json
*.local.json

# Misplaced MCP config (a token leaked here once and was purged from
# history; this entry is preventive).
.mcp.json
mcp.json

# Windows shortcuts (.lnk) and Internet Shortcuts (.url) — embed
# metadata that fingerprints the host (LocalBasePath, MachineID, user
# SID via target). Keep them off the repo even if their target is
# benign. Convenience links to %LocalAppData%\Deckle\, the auto-memory
# directory, etc., live next to the working tree but stay local.
*.lnk
*.url

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Runtime artifacts
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Temporary audio file written during recording.
**/temp.wav

# Crash dumps and ad hoc diagnostic files.
.tmp/
**/.tmp-*
*.dmp
*.mdmp
crash-*.log
crashdumps/

# File-based crash logs (see HudComposition.DebugLog pattern). The
# folder itself stays versioned so the path exists when code writes
# to it.
logs/*
!logs/.gitkeep

# Top-level run log (live tail captured by build-run.ps1).
run.log

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Benchmark — runtime artifacts, never versioned
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#   telemetry/  raw Deckle capture (corpus JSONL + WAVs, latency, app log).
#               Layout: <slug>/corpus.jsonl, <slug>/audio/*.wav, …
#   reports/    per-run benchmark output (last_<name>_run.{json,txt},
#               per-experiment snapshots). Regenerated each run.
#   logs/       step-by-step log of the benchmark script itself —
#               kept so a crashed run can be resumed.
#   results.tsv journal at benchmark/ root, one row per experiment.
benchmark/**/__pycache__/
benchmark/telemetry/
benchmark/reports/
benchmark/logs/
benchmark/results.tsv

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Python tooling — caches and virtualenvs (benchmark/ + ad hoc scripts)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.tox/
*.egg-info/
venv/
.venv/
env/
ENV/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Node / npx caches — preventive (MCP servers run via npx may write here)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

node_modules/
.npm/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Test / coverage output
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

TestResults/
coverage/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Claude Code runtime state and local-only customisation
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tracked agent / skill / instruction files stay versioned — only
# runtime state and personal-only customisation are excluded.

.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/.session*

# Worktrees created via Claude Code's EnterWorktree tool. The directory
# itself is a registered git worktree (its content is not git-tracked
# in the parent), but excluding the path here prevents `git status`
# from ever surfacing it as untracked, and prevents accidental
# `git add .` pollution.
.claude/worktrees/

# Personal-workflow skills not meant for the public repo.
.claude/skills/benchmark-loop/